  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MiniMax-M2.1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"382\" data-imgfileid=\"100017413\" data-ratio=\"0.3296296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e5a59ff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqRTNqgePIpQxiaSgHFFJaabyDwq5GylVpbQoCocj3gP3QcLLaasW7WzwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MiniMax-M2.1是一个开源的高性能Agent模型，旨在打破高性能Agent必须封闭的刻板印象。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型经过优化，专注于代码生成、工具使用、指令跟随和长远规划等任务。MiniMax-M2.1支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多语言软件开发自动化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">复杂的多步骤办公工作流执行</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，帮助开发者构建下一代自主应用程序。该模型透明、可控且易于访问，致力于将真正的智能带给更多人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/minimax-m2-gguf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/minimax-m2-gguf2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Qwen-Doc</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3101851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"360\" data-imgfileid=\"100017414\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44605a83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqRsVX944LhfhDk0fCmuo2x2Ariaf9ibp22DM3coQJdSkNosdmoXlj7XYiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Qwen-Doc是一个开源项目库，专注于文档人工智能，由通义智文团队开发和维护。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在整合围绕长上下文理解、文档解析和基于文档的智能Agent等前沿技术的探索和实践。通过开源模型、数据和方法论，Qwen-Doc致力于提升大语言模型在处理和理解复杂文档方面的能力，以促进社区的成长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qwendoc\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qwendoc</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Iceberg</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"494\" data-imgfileid=\"100017417\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d417625&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqRpGjKibTct152JzZtkdia8V4CclvF1srVr3FLtlcxXKsWRFdUpib7KrCUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Iceberg是一个全面的基准套件，用于在现实应用环境中对向量相似性搜索（VSS）方法进行端到端评估</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。它涵盖了7个不同的数据集，涉及图像分类、面部识别、文本检索和推荐系统等关键领域。每个数据集包含100万到1亿个向量，并附有任务特定的标签和指标，使得可以在完整的应用管道中评估检索算法，而不仅仅是在孤立的召回速度场景中。Iceberg对13种最先进的VSS算法进行基准测试，并使用任务中心的性能指标对其重新排名，揭示了与传统召回/速度排名的显著偏差。此外，Iceberg提出了一种可解释的决策树，以指导从业者为特定工作负载选择和调整VSS方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/iceberg\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/iceberg</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：SCOPE</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"390\" data-imgfileid=\"100017415\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e14ff80e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqRPibnmEs2ugibG6fpFo8pPzD56aGZW1b7Xb6HBbzuDbicd7VVQvnwiaNPmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SCOPE是一个自动化提示优化框架，通过从Agent执行轨迹中学习，将静态Agent提示转化为自我进化系统。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">SCOPE自动合成执行轨迹中的指导方针，并持续改进Agent性能，而无需手动编写提示。该框架支持OpenAI、Anthropic等100多个提供商，具备自动学习、双流记忆、最佳选择、记忆优化等功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/scope\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/scope</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FinSight</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.587037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"682\" data-imgfileid=\"100017416\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83c17149&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqROnqykNyjibYW5ibOLX1SAZVubx2MicuF0DGLuGxuqqxAL2XIadj5M7trw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FinSight是一个多Agent研究系统，旨在自动化整个金融研究过程，从数据收集和分析到生成具备专业图表和深刻见解的出版级报告。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">用户只需输入一个股票代码，即可一键生成全面的研究报告。该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">透明的分析链</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">严格的引用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，确保高文本忠实度和可验证的见解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/finsight\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/finsight</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：RLinf v0.2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"404\" data-imgfileid=\"100017418\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71b6e872&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwZuCmkB8sFy5lswQMayRqRaxMeOfLzHXxErbNLoe32DJ76avag5spZBpuSBqbpz3Xd0qhUttaG1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★RLinf v0.2是一款面向真机强化学习路线的全异构、全异步开源尝鲜版强化学习基础设施。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它创新性地将机器人视作与GPU同级的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可灵活配置资源</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，用户仅需编写</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">YAML</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">文件，即可实现异地真机的便捷接入与模型映射，实现 “像使用GPU一样使用机器人” 的高效体验。该版本支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">全异构软硬件集群配置</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，适配端云协同的复杂真机训练场景，同时搭载</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">全异步off-policy算法框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，通过端云训推解耦提升数据利用率与训练效率。依托Macro-to-Micro Flow编程范式，RLinf v0.2兼顾系统灵活性与高效性，为具身智能探索出 “Scaling 真机” 的全新路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rlinf\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rlinf</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
